al/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a1ba7ae5c8bc1e86cd8cb06601dc4c8bd46779","tid":1767394,"uid":71635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc7ae5e52a6b2ec84b2f47e90bf9e43aa899f338","tid":1767394,"uid":76310,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不留活口和證據意味着將來被起訴定罪的機會較低，而這也比較不會招致國際間的反感</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即使任何人或組織生疑，也找不到確鑿的證據取信於人</span><br />\n<br />\n屌你, 同香港一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"肯定過萬人連家人已被消失"},{"pid":"9cff6b282aa4bd3becfa9569cb60c3745b71c897","tid":1767394,"uid":255940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"如果冇打仗就乜都係假<br />\n講到尾都係因為軍政府收皮<br />\n係咪咁理解"},{"pid":"67739100e5d2913768a0e0e9630a219dff953f0d","tid":1767394,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"亨利&middot;基辛格、傑拉爾德&middot;福特所領導的美國政府所知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又係親共基辛格<br />\n早排先去完支那<br />\n原來係擁抱賤人嘅賤人"},{"pid":"40b03b969708393f5fc8990d55f54ebde26a1c4f","tid":1767394,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724afcfe8d20d2d36c2d68ddbc40a0401f69d120","tid":1767394,"uid":178092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"everyone please be careful"},{"pid":"9eeded4e425984f04678345c19119e8b6c3f3bcb","tid":1767394,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3301fe102ab81fe96609b14f6a9102ec4ca43437","tid":1767394,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:52:40.000Z","msg":"當「被失蹤」成為常態：阿根廷的骯髒戰爭與五月廣場母親的反抗<br />\n<br />\n而在1977年，阿根廷就已經出現了一個拯救其子女及向國家討回公道的團體：五月廣場母親（Mothers of the Plaza de Mayo）。<br />\n<br />\n國家恐怖主義與「骯髒戰爭」時期<br />\n阿根廷現時是一個成熟的民主國家，但在半個世紀前，阿根廷的掌權者仍以威權主義治國。在經過近20年的經濟停頓、軍人及文人政府頻繁交替後，伊莎貝爾．貝隆（Isabel Mart&iacute;nez de Per&oacute;n）在1973年以副總統的身分掌權，並在1974年成為代理總統。在她和社會福利部長何塞．洛佩斯．雷加（Jos&eacute; L&oacute;pez Rega）的領導及支持下，右翼軍事組織「阿根廷反共同盟」（Argentine Anticommunist Alliance）以止暴制亂（註）、重建國家的名義，大肆抓捕及殺害異己。除了針對共產主義者及游擊隊外，年輕人、工會成員、不同界別的專業人士也會無故被捕或失蹤，而當中的國家暴力亦比以前更普遍及有組織，屬國家恐怖主義（state terrorism）的開端。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:03:11.000Z","msg":"香港已經進入state terrorism"},{"pid":"156b90a3a1d3f4a53e0813dae8721311d9a4afc2","tid":1767394,"uid":57480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:05:41.000Z","msg":"pull"},{"pid":"6686d7d65c0c5f041231ed7692e490eaad7e8484","tid":1767394,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"大家諗下有乜計, 防止手足被消失"},{"pid":"bf93e6ef3beaf6c99147d59ca0f6b922641530d4","tid":1767394,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"就算抗爭完咗，共黨不倒，香港都係大把會慢慢失蹤"},{"pid":"a28979ef86b21d61399003b3bb889a260282beb8","tid":1767394,"uid":231514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3948e839847eeb3ef57bd878ee7fb4e036ca018","tid":1767394,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"大家諗下有乜計, 防止手足被消失"},{"pid":"c3c80e84091a846d25ede869cb41cc848e21155c","tid":1767394,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:32:46.000Z","msg":"所以槍權真係好重要<br />\n<br />\n係港豬先會反槍權, 話只比毅進仔拿槍係好安全<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/NG69XZnZ/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FNG69XZnZ%2Fimage.png&h=8b610b74&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97f075297dc63c3cf0d5aced6414a4aef56c7824","tid":1767394,"uid":238040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:33:15.000Z","msg":"好多字，整合啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb17892388b8fbc486dddd5dd81c8f3bf8d23292","tid":1767394,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T11:33:52.000Z","msg":"「重開」又有香港人失蹤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755555</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有個 tg 失蹤人士channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/FindingHKer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFindingHKer&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0Ksfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=c4507e82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/FindingHKer</a><br />\n<br />\nfb group<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/434115767233839/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F434115767233839%2F&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0Ksfo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=f49bed24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/434115767233839/</a><br />\n<br />\n￼大家仲記唔記得<br />\n太子站搵朋友個姨姨？<br />\n<br />\n831 搵失蹤姨姨 (之後有「認罪」錄音)<br />\n［勁恐怖］太子站前上鏡受訪問後<br />\n被逼錄音同可能已被自殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577080</a>"},{"pid":"9ac448675f7332365108b2a7ae78375614e07aad","tid":1767394,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"阿根庭軍政府都冇香港黑警咁垃圾"},{"pid":"57fe64a0a1bbe7a62f4e97dd7ad7294d411f91c1","tid":1767394,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75522f1b992e8f410a8b5481e923626edfd7b6ea","tid":1767394,"uid":120678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b41dbf9eecffcbb0ef3fc60e9031ecc7f15f9de7","tid":1767394,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"唓<br />\n呢個白人國家都算那渣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T12:48:45.000Z","msg":"所以阿根廷由發達國家倒退成落後國家<br />\n目前為止全世界唯一一個例子，希臘都冇佢威"},{"pid":"8b9ed262fc50fef93e75decdb4bfa008e271c070","tid":1767394,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"唔想手足死得不明不白 但唔知點做"},{"pid":"54146a46bcf110e9d001221fbfa66443503d882c","tid":1767394,"uid":47548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ba3093330da11ec711694720316fb291a5a413","tid":1767394,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"「阿根廷反共同盟」（Argentine Anticommunist Alliance）以止暴制亂（註）、重建國家的名義(止暴制亂)<br />\n<br />\n至於受虐至死的受害者，政府不會把遺體交還家屬，只會草草埋葬以毀屍滅迹，因此家屬一直得不到任何音信(一定係無可疑)<br />\n<br />\n「失蹤者」之中有超過八成是16-35歲的青年人及中年人(死好多年青人)<br />\n<br />\n政府應對的方式不是退讓，而是賦予政府機關更大的權力及武力(一樣)<br />\n<br />\n不留活口和證據意味着將來被起訴定罪的機會較低，而這也比較不會招致國際間的反感. 即使任何人或組織生疑，也找不到確鑿的證據取信於人(好多人話要FC喎, 唔係就唔信, 結果中晒正苦計. 當年阿根廷軍正苦就係咁殺左幾萬人)<br />\n<br />\n政府繼續進行其心理戰。政府一方面繼續否認，並標籤這些母親們為「瘋婦」(人格攻擊,)<br />\n<br />\n屌你, 直情同而家香港一模一樣"},{"pid":"98144e5fdb0a344237c08e49dd572485d881f917","tid":1767394,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKpujjg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKpujjg.jpg&h=493bba6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[提案] 其實香港人應該同港共政府割蓆....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eCxnwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eCxnwS</a>"},{"pid":"496920e25e241c5e7ae849467f10d703aa8dd6f8","tid":1767394,"uid":205347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T13:49:41.000Z","msg":"[整合] &ndash; 發夢你要知道的十